biz.paluch.spinach.cluster

Class NodeIdAwareSocketAddressSupplier

  • java.lang.Object
    • biz.paluch.spinach.impl.ClusterAwareNodeSupport
      • biz.paluch.spinach.impl.HelloClusterSocketAddressSupplier
        • biz.paluch.spinach.cluster.NodeIdAwareSocketAddressSupplier
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ConnectionAware, SocketAddressSupplier, Supplier<SocketAddress>

    public class NodeIdAwareSocketAddressSupplier
extends HelloClusterSocketAddressSupplier
    This mechanism allows to set a preferred node Id for next HELLO handshake. If the setPreferredNodeIdPrefix(String) is set, the selection mechanism tries to provide a SocketAddress from the preferred node.
